ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of RHODA KOKIAPIK of Inukjuak, Nunavik, Quebec, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Sara Vered, whose term has expired.
